Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,5,,泪雨的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的特别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在这个样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没有会输的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放状态持续时间过长的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体就会渐渐地被咒印给侵蚀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被侵蚀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会永远失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这副身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来已经没时间再磨磨蹭蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左手的感觉…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的这股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎也伴随着风险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称做终结之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此为舞台不是正合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过闲聊已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那差不多也该做个终结了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止的战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面是第七班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春野樱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和鸣人在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和佐助在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少别拖我的后腿哦 废物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为因为因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师你说过啊 所以这家伙才…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是三人小组吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 我们三个是一个集体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧 胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧 胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想和你战斗一场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…想要和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想眼睁睁地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着重要的同伴死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通灵之术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:07:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是笑呢 是兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到能跟你在这里决斗并且取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖后腿的居然也如此狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会一辈子都当拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点出招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交手之前 把护额戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 快点戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没有本事弄伤我的额头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们作为木叶忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对等决斗的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少自以为是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股查克拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气味不会消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近了 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是来迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能及时赶到 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定拼尽了全力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸总是会提到你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我是独一无二的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为你必须超越的壁垒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会和你一起共存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.25,0:17:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使被你憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是万花筒写轮眼的开眼者之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那需要特殊的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉自己最亲密的…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终结之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人和佐助竟然在这里战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够讽刺的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着这条河流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛让我目睹了一场永无止尽的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像建造了木叶村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化身为这两尊石像的人的命运一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人和佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这两人一息尚存…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:19:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉自己最亲密的…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会按你说的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用自己的方法获得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用自己的方法…超越你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨…停了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这骤雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭气味已经无法追踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 比起去追佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是鸣人更为优先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情变得有趣起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过会把佐助带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一生的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 一切都还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会信守约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是常说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:22:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一向言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:22:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这就是我的忍道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未能信守的约定
